Paper: hep-th/9406170

Date: 1994-06-24

Title: From geometric quantization to Moyal quantization

Authors: Jose M. Gracia-Bondia and Joseph C. Varilly

Comments: 7 two-column pages, RevTeX, UCR--FM--03--94

Journal-ref: J.Math.Phys. 36 (1995) 2691-2701

We show how the Moyal product of phase-space functions, and the Weylcorrespondence between symbols and operator kernels, may be obtained directlyusing the procedures of geometric quantization, applied to the symplecticgroupoid constructed by ``doubling'' the phase space.